					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Have you tried using a debugging emulator (FCEUX on Windows, Nintendulator, Mesen)? It should help you narrow down what's going wrong.<br /><br />Guessing, the most likely reason something doesn't work when MMC3 is that your reset function isn't in the very last 8 KiB of PRG; the specific banks mapped to $8000-$DFFF aren't guaranteed on power-up.</div>

