						<div class="postbody">$6010 bytes is a valid size for &quot;NROM 128&quot; boards. $10 header+$4000 PRG + $2000 CHR.<br /><br />If there is only 1 bank of PRG ROM, it is loaded to $8000-bfff and mirrored at $c000-ffff.<br /><br />I would expect it to work.</div>

					
