						<div class="postbody">For ram I use enums:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">.enum $6000<br />SomeVar:&nbsp; &nbsp; .db 0<br />SomeWord:&nbsp; &nbsp;.dw 0<br />SomeArray:&nbsp; .dsb SIZE_OF_ARRAY<br />.ende<br /></div><br /><br />For an 8k bank:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;.base $8000<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;; code/data<br />IF $ &gt; $9FFF<br />ERROR &quot;Bank overflow&quot;<br />ENDIF<br />&nbsp; .org $A000<br /></div><br /><br />Repeat for however many banks you have, changing the addresses as needed.</div>

